# Custom Non-Commercial License

**Copyright © 2026 Werner Deuermeier**

## About This Project

This interactive learning tool was created for the Castagnari Benny C/G (3-row, Heim tuning) diatonic accordion. It combines traditional accordion pedagogy with modern web technology to help students visualize button layouts, practice chords and scales, and understand bellows technique.

